You can use `Flux.merge` to resolve publishers in parallel.

&gt;Merge data from Publisher sequences contained in an array / vararg into an interleaved merged sequence. Unlike `concat`, sources are subscribed to eagerly.

```
.flatMapMany(x -&gt; Flux.merge(
        getB1(x.getRids()).map(B1::getCid), //Stage 2
        getB2(x.getRids()).map(B2::getCid)  //Stage 3
    )
)
.collectList()
```

